(27787, 'Swixtobram 0.3% eye drops 5 ml', 'سويكساوبرام 0.3% قطرة للعين 5مل', '', '7', 'Tobramycin', 'Chemipharm', 'Drops', 'نقط', '', 'Antibiotic.aminoglycoside', '0.3%', 'Inhaled tobramycin is indicated for the management of cystic fibrosis patients with _Pseudomonas aeruginosa_, but is not recommended in patients under six years of age, those with forced expiratory volume in 1 second (FEV<sub>1</sub>) <25 or >80% predicted, or in those with _Burkholderia cepacia_.[L32739,L45364]
